BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 748 Tm (I would choose a **hybrid model**:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 725 Tm (- Main workflows stay click-based and predictable) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 710 Tm (- AI acts as an assistant, not the primary interface) Tj ET
