BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 626 Tm (Why:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 603 Tm (- Operations users usually prefer speed and reliability over chat-first UX) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 588 Tm (- A fully AI-driven app is harder to test and less predictable) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 573 Tm (- Hybrid gives AI value without making the product feel fragile) Tj ET
