BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 72 434 Tm (- Easier to share API patterns and UI decisions with the web app) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 411 Tm (I would only choose native apps first if offline support, camera/scanner features, or) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 396 Tm (platform-specific SDKs were a major requirement.) Tj ET
